{{Infobox serial killer |name=Gustavo Romero Tercero |image= |caption= |birthname=Gustavo Romero Tercero |alias=The Valdepeñas Killer |birth_date=1970 |birth_place=[[Valdepeñas]], [[Spain]] |death_date= |cause= |victims=3 |country=Spain |states= |beginyear=1993 |endyear=1998 |apprehended= |penalty=103 years in prison }}
'''Gustavo Romero Tercero''' (born 1970), also known as "The Valdepeñas Killer", is a Spanish armed robber and rapist. He killed a couple after the woman recognized him in 1993 and another woman in 1998 after accidentally hitting her with his car, fearing that a possible investigation would link him to the other crimes. He confessed and was sentenced to 103 years in prison in 2003, after his ex-wife denounced him.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.elmundo.es/elmundo/2005/04/21/sociedad/1114074425.html | title=ondenan a 103 años de prisión a Gustavo Romero por el asesinato de tres personas en Valdepeñas | publisher=El Mundo | date=April 22, 2005 | accessdate=February 9, 2014}}</ref>
